Combine dry pudding mix, coconut, milk and extract. Drop by heaping teaspoonfuls, 1 inch apart, into 30 mounds on parchment-covered baking sheets. Bake 12 to 15 min. or until firm. Immediately transfer macaroons from baking sheets to wire racks; press 1 nut into top of each. Cool completely. Microwave chocolate as directed on package. Dip bottoms of macaroons in chocolate; place on sheet of waxed paper. Let stand until chocolate is firm.